summary: Replaces Skyrims soundtrack with music by the very talented composer, Vindsvept.
descriptionHtml:
This is a very early version of a mod I plan to work on in my spare time. I have played Skyrim for 1000+ hours and have slowly gotten tired with the "vanilla" music. 

The I discovered the very talented composer, Vindsvept. Using Vindsvept's music I plan to create a mod which replaces the original score with a appropriate song from Vindsvept. 

[b]Vindsvept Links:[/b]
www.vindsvept.com
https://www.youtube.com/user/Vindsvept/featured

Go support him as he has done 99% of the work for this mod. I just fill in the gaps and package nicely.

[b]Disclaimer:[/b]
This mod is extremely early in development and therefore I do not recommend using it yet. This page is currently for my friends to help me with the mod.

I am a complete N00b at modding so this is also a learning experience for myself.
author: Bean438
